## Design Overview

Netflix UK features a dark, cinematic design system optimized for video content consumption. The design emphasizes a bold red accent color (#E50914) against deep black backgrounds, creating high contrast and visual impact. The typography uses a custom Netflix Sans Variable font with clean, modern styling. The layout is minimalist with focus on content, featuring gradient overlays on hero sections and smooth transitions throughout. The design is fully responsive with carefully crafted breakpoints that maintain visual hierarchy across all device sizes.

